comment: In a parade , three girls in green uniforms and green and yellow feathers are dancing down the middle of a street .

comment: An older gentleman is selling produce out of the back of his truck as a woman peruses his products .

comment: Three men at a bus stop , one man is turned around to tie his shoe as one man stands in front of the other who is sitting on a bench talking to him .

comment: A group of fisherman peer out at the city across the river as they wait for the fish to bite .

comment: A girl in a purple dress is sitting on furniture with red pillows , while smiling for the camera .

comment: A man holding an girl in a bathing suit over his shoulder on a busy beach with a Ferris wheel in the background .

comment: Two men putting a cover over a makeshift boat with a couch on it .

comment: A man in a black hat and shorts adjusting a mesh tent outdoors .

comment: A man in swim trunks is in a shallow portion of a lake with his hand on a portion of a small dock .

comment: A woman wearing a white blouse , eyeglasses , and floppy hat is reading a book next to a small body of water .

comment: Two men sit on a pontoon boat holding oars and wearing hats .

comment: A guy sitting in a tube in the water .

comment: A man is taking a bath in something that looks like a sink but is a round tub .

comment: A man in t-shirt and shorts kneels near a line of plastic crates containing duct tape , bags , and other supplies .

comment: Person dressed in black stands next to a white car that has inter tubes and a couch stacked on top of it .

comment: A brunette female , in yellow tank top , paisley printed skirt , hairy legs , seated on a blue sofa , reading a book .

comment: Children play with a remote-control boat in a pond with a boat house .

comment: A man wearing a straw hat and a red bandanna has fallen asleep sitting up outside on a couch .

comment: A woman holding a magazine , is touching the outside of a wooden window frame .

comment: A man wearing red pants without a top is holding on to a ladder .

comment: Four adults near the edge of a body of water ; the landscape is hilly and rocky , with mountains in the background .

comment: A belly dancer wearing a red and gold costume stands with her arms above her head .

comment: A man in a red and black outfit is sitting on a high platform with a strange look on his face and a yellow wig .
